{
  "chapter": 13,
  "chapter_summary": "寒夜星光下，马如龙追逐神秘卖花女却追不上，发现对方竟是大婉假扮。大婉身世武功来历皆成谜，绝大师、玉道人等顶尖高手对她畏惧有加。大婉带马如龙潜入县城衙门，官差对他们视而不见。二人来到仵作验尸房，大婉让马如龙查看布单下一名赤裸的绝美女子——正是那卖花女。大婉设计让卖花女低估自己，将其制服。卖花女并未死去，大婉说她与马如龙日后必有关联。随后大婉又带马如龙去见江南俞五，说俞五正在做一件谁都猜不到的事。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是不是不想让我看见你，不想让我知道你是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可惜我已经知道你是谁了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你本来就应该知道的。因为你并不太笨。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我知道你的胆子一向不小，所以这次我要带你到一个奇怪的地方去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "去干什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "去见一个人，一个非常奇怪的女人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "我见过她？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "大概见过一次。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "你说的就是那个卖花女？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你果然不笨，却不知你敢不敢去见他？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你不后悔？见到了她之后，无论发生什么事，你都不后悔？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "我已经做了这么多应该后悔的事，再多做一件有什么关系？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "没有关系，一点关系都没有。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "喂，你有没有看见我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "官差",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "刚才是不是有人在说话？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "官差",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "官差",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你有没有看见什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "官差",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有，连个鬼影子都没有看见。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你就算在他们面前翻斤斗，他们也看不见的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "因为他们都是明白人，都明白应该在什么时候装袭作哑。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你知不知道这院子是什么地方？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "这就是仵作验尸的地方，只要县境内有凶杀冤死的人，尸体一定要先送到这里，让仵作检验死因。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "你要带我来见的人，就在这房子里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你为什么不自己进去看看？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "她死了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "看起来好像是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "是你杀了她？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "她一直看不起我，一直认为她的本事比我大，随时都可以把我打倒，我一看见她就逃走，也正是要她低估我。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "她果然低估了我，所以现在我站着，她已倒下，看起来就好像死了一样。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "只不过是看起来像死了一样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "其实她还没有死？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你为什么不自己去看看？看得清楚些。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你看，她是不是死了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "只看了一眼，你当然看不出她的死活，但是你至少应该看得出，像她这么美的女人并不多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "那么你就应该看出她还没有死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "因为她实在太美了，连我都舍不得让她死，就算我心里很想杀了她，也不忍下手的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你为什么叹气？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "因为我发现我自己实在很笨。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你怎么会发现的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "现在我已经看过她，也相信她还没有死，可是我反而越来越不明白了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "不明白什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "我认不认得她？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "不认得。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "她跟我有什么关系？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "直到现在还没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "那么你为什么一定要我来看她？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "因为你们现在虽然还没有关系，以后却一定会有的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "以后会有什么关系？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "有些事我现在还不能告诉你，但是我可以保证，我要你做的事，绝不会让你后悔的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "现在你又准备要我干什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我准备再带你去见一个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "去见谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "一个很喜欢你的人，你好像也有点喜欢他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "你怎么知道，我喜欢他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "只要见过他的人，想要不喜欢他都很难。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "江南俞五？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "除了他还有谁呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "他也在这里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "就在对面。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "在干什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "他在干什么，你一辈子都猜不到的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    }
  ],
